Text.Value: Hunting for anything?
Leave.
Leave.
*Riaow!*
Hunting for anything?
Mr Dekarios! Heavens, fancy seeing you here!
I have missed you!
Leave.
See you in camp later, hmm?
I may, or I may not. Depends what you have to offer in return. I have very high standards, mind.
I'd like to know if you have any other interesting objects to trade.
It appears my old friend Tara here has found some objects that might interest us. Care to trade?
*Riaow!*

EditorData.SFXTags: [GwenLee] Cat needs a meow that sounds like she's explaining she found something.

Text.Value: Have you got any other magic objects you'd be willing to part with?
Lovely to see you, sir.
That will be all, thank you!
Mr Dekarios! Heavens, fancy seeing you here!
She says that will be all.
*Meow!*
I've a nose for the things, in fact. But I get bored of déjà vu, so don't expect to see me again.
Let's see her wares.
Tara! That can't be you, can it?

Synopsis: Player approaches Tara and sees she is carrying an item. Player tries to convince Tara to give the item over. If Gale is in party he will be favoured speaker and will recognize Tara and why she has a magic item with her.
